OL,7,F"I think it (the Bill) is a step in
OL,8,Fthe right direction, it's a really
OL,9,Fgood positive step that victims'
OL,10,Ffamilies voices are being heard and
OL,11,Fbeing valued as well and listened to
OL,12,Fby parliament," Jebina Islam said.
OL,14,F"I think with violence against young
OL,15,Fwomen and girls we are going through
OL,16,Fan epidemic.
OL,18,F"We need more education for young
OL,19,Fchildren at school so they have an
OL,20,Funderstanding of what's wrong and
OL,21,Fright," she added.
