OL,3,CSister of Sabina Nessa welcomes plans
OL,4,Cto punish criminals who avoid
OL,5,Csentencing
OL,7,FJustice minister Alex Davies-Jones
OL,8,Fsaid: "I would like to thank the
OL,9,Fremarkable families of Olivia Pratt-
OL,10,FKorbel, Jan Mustafa, Sabina Nessa and
OL,11,FZara Aleena and countless others who
OL,12,Fhave campaigned tirelessly for
OL,13,Foffenders to have to face the reality
OL,14,Fof their crimes by attending their
OL,15,Fsentencing.
OL,17,F"Justice isn't optional ` we'll make
OL,18,Fsure criminals face their victims."
