OL,7,FThe Bill also plans to restrict
OL,8,Fparental responsibility from child sex
OL,9,Foffenders who committed serious crimes
OL,10,Fagainst their own child to boost
OL,11,Fprotection for victims.
OL,13,FThe move will stop them being able to
OL,14,Fask for updates on their child's
OL,15,Fschooling or trying to interfere in
OL,16,Ftheir life.
